    <p><b>Quick Start:</b></p>
        <p>&nbsp;</p>
    <p>First, try to find an entity using one or more of the following search techniques:</p>
        <p>&nbsp;</p>
    <ol id="font81">
      <li>Search by Company or Organization name and state. If too many records are returned, try adding a City.<br /><br /></li>
      <li>Search by Address, City and State.<br /><br /></li>
      <li>Search by CLIA Number or CLIA Number and State.<br /><br/></li>
    </ol>
